## Context

- Forty-fourth run — Covered 8 projects with 10 new journal entries and 4 new tasks.
- Journal #1350 (pten-loss-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
  - **ICMT validated as SL target in PTEN-deficient TNBC (Exp Hematol Oncol 2025, PMID 41507994):** CRISPR screen + cysmethynil xenograft PoC. Mechanism: disrupts PIP3-GEF-Rac1-PI3K feedback. Orthogonal to PI3K/AKT/mTOR.
- Journal #1351 (rb1-loss-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
  - **RB1+ATR/PKMYT1 SL in breast cancer (SciTranslMed 2025, PMID 41442499):** PDX regression. New SL pair complementing CDK2/Aurora/CHK1/WEE1. Relevant for CDK4/6i-resistant patients.
- Journal #1352 (rb1-loss-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
  - **CDK2 biomarkers + BLU-222 synergy (NatComm 2025):** P16+CycE1 governs CDK2 vulnerability. 4-gene signature (CCND1/CCNE1/RB1/CDKN2A) predicts CDK2+CDK4/6 combo response. BLU-222+CDK4/6i durable regression in 8 resistant PDX models.
- Journal #1353 (pancancer-ferroptosis-atlas):
  - **SAT1/polyamine ferroptosis pathway — KEAP1-dependent (NatComm 2025):** Polyamines sensitize KRAS-MUT/KEAP1-WT cells to KRAS inhibitors via SAT1. KEAP1-MUT resistant due to JNK-NRF2-SAT1 axis.
- Journal #1354 (pancancer-ferroptosis-atlas):
  - **GLS1 inhibition reverses KEAP1-MUT ferroptosis resistance (AACR 2026 B013) + NatRevClinOncol 2026 ferroptosis review.** Combined with SAT1 data: polyamine supp for KEAP1-WT, GLS1i for KEAP1-MUT.
- Journal #1355 (wrn-msi-pancancer-atlas):
  - **WRN structural cycle (CommBiol 2026) + resistance divergence (bioRxiv Jan 2026):** HRO761/VVD-214 lock WRN in off-DNA states via distinct mechanisms. Resistance profiles diverge — alternating inhibitors may overcome resistance. DNA-PK as combo partner.
- Journal #1356 (pancancer-mtap-prmt5-atlas):
  - **Vopimetostat updated data:** 27% ORR pan-tumor (16 types), 49% ORR histology-agnostic (41 pts), 25% ORR 2L PDAC. Pivotal PDAC trial (~300 pts) 2026. Combo with RAS(ON) inhibitors + ERAS-0015 enrolling.
- Journal #1358 (crc-kras-dependencies):
  - **ERAS-0015 Q4/FY2025 update (Mar 12, 2026):** Confirmed PRs, worldwide rights secured, H1 2026 mono data IMMINENT. $258.8M raised. ERAS-4001 H2 2026.
- Journal #1359 (tp53-hotspot-allele-dependencies):
  - **Rezatapopt PYNNACLE Phase 2 protocol published:** ~114 pts, ~70 sites, enrollment completing Q1 2026. 34% ORR in 8 tumor types. NDA Q1 2027.
- Journal #1360 (cdkn2a-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
  - **CDK4/6i mitigates TP53-mutant clonal hematopoiesis (NatGenetics 2026):** Trilaciclib prevents CH clone expansion. Safety angle for CDK4/6i expansion in CDKN2A-deleted cancers.
- Tasks created: research_director #934 (ferroptosis SAT1/GLS1 KEAP1-stratified), #935 (CDK2 4-gene signature RB1+CDKN2A), #937 (RB1 ATR/PKMYT1 mapping), #938 (PTEN ICMT cross-reference).
- Task #151 — vopimetostat per-histology ORR still pending. Histology-agnostic cohort now 49% ORR but tumor-type breakdowns still not disclosed.
